member.summary:
Looks up a localized string similar to Amiga BootBlock Reader ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ ABR is a program that reads and writes the bootblock area of Amiga disks.
With this program you can: ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ - View and identify bootblocks from ADF's and saved bootblock files - Batch scan your ADF files to find viruses / unknown bootblocks - Save bootblocks to your PC harddisk from ADF's for backup purposes / collection - Install a variety of standard AmigaOS bootblocks to ADF's to fix booting problems - [rest of string was truncated]";.
